nodes.text: Asset I-4 was a member of the intelligence network that served the independent operative known as The Shroud during the Galactic War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. Around 3637 BBY, I-4 was dispatched by the Shroud to investigate the recent deaths of Assets I-12, I-32, and I-40.
